title: Add profile policy authorization and denial tests
---
Acceptance: room_profile_authz or equivalent shared helper gates every privileged surface through existing channel admin identity (Admin.is_admin/channel_admins) for CLI/slash/admin paths; authz matrix covers grant mutation, policy mutation, CWD/workspace changes, budgets, codebase bindings, routine create/edit/delete/trigger, ledger read/export/retention, and profile bind/rebind/delete; guests cannot mutate these surfaces; denied access is audited and errors tell operators which admin action is required. Files: src/admin.ml, command/slash/admin handlers, tests.